//create new user
SQL> create user appuser IDENTIFIED BY app123;
User created.
NOTE: IF previous user with this name is already created by any student on that system then we can
drop that user by following query: drop user appuser; otherwise will get error msg
Like username appuser conflicts with another user or rolename.
and again try to create otherwise instead of appuser take any another name to create user.
==================================================================================
==========================================================
//grant privileges to new user
SQL> grant CONNECT, RESOURCE TO appuser;

Grant succeeded.
